parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
J3 X component of the magnetic-field in nT.                             
      X is in the Jovian equatorial plane along the line through the          
      System 3 (1997), positive away from Jupiter.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
J3 Y component of the magnetic-field in nT.                             
      Y completes the right handed set (Z x X).

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
J3 Z component of the magnetic-field in nT.                             
      Z is parallel to Jovian spin axis, Omega, positive north of             
      the equator.

parameters.name: BTOTAL
parameters.description:
Average value of the full-resolution magnetic-field magnitudes          
      calculated over the averaging interval in nT. Note that this value      
      may differ slightly from the square root of the sum of the squares      
      of the averaged field components.

parameters.name: NPTS
parameters.description: Number of points in the average.
